ygData.messageBody:
Is anyone running EQ under NT? If so, could you please tell me how? My
friend wants to join us all but can't get EQ to run under NT. He is pulling
out what little is left of his hair. LOL. Seriously, we would appreciate
any help/advise you might be able to supply. Thank you.

Also, Kachine will be selling netted armor at the Festival on Sunday and
will be buying Tentacle whips. Problem is, she doesn't know the selling
prices these items bring. Anyone know the going price on these items? She
has netted pieces for: neck, face, head, arm, shoulders, chest, back and
legs (only one wristband). Thanks.
